{"tid":601656,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：香港去年千萬富翁增15%至6.8萬人","createTime":"2018-03-22T11:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T12:39:38.000Z","uid":70274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"047827754e5d51e750750320dab0a967a00e52b0","tid":601656,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:30:31.000Z","msg":"AASTOCKS<br />\n<br />\n花旗調查報告發現，去年本港擁有1,000萬元或以上流動資產的千萬富翁達68,000人，按年增長15%。本港千萬富翁的投資資產組合分配中，仍然維持現金比例約36%。本港39%的千萬富翁持有海外物業，預期樓價上升的比例由2015年的11%上升至去年的38%。<br />\n本港與中國內地富裕人士的整體資產分佈相若，當中超過70%的總資產皆投放在物業，當中本港富裕人士所持有的海外物業則較多，平均每人1.3個物業，內地富豪則僅得0.7個。(vi/a)~<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=G4MbdYmg0nSFIzY5CecUO2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=92f3e805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"a9216640a8fd730caeb06586da796a4806b1dd79","tid":601656,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60102123a58bb25fb399446db559854aef52165e","tid":601656,"uid":67201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9216640a8fd730caeb06586da796a4806b1dd79","tid":601656,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:37:38.000Z","msg":"百萬都富翁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92baced9e8a1820a8d94f928ecdbe87d9d7ed656","tid":601656,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9216640a8fd730caeb06586da796a4806b1dd79","tid":601656,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:35:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"計埋自己果棟三層樓咁濟<br />\n跟本咩都唔洗做就夠食<br />\n唔通日日番工叫富豪"},{"pid":"2bef1e36b85abe8b5742d70dfac725143f6de9db","tid":601656,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0